Name: Goblin treasure
About the game: Goblin Treasure is a casual arcade game in which you play the role of a goblin treasure hunter. Collecting diamonds while traveling across various boards. Your main goal is to collect as many diamonds as possible while avoiding goblins and traps. Main features: - 5 levels - 3 levels of difficulty - big boards
